Etunatetap Mordekai


1  [
1  ] Ki ng'at Laitoryat aisuruut eng' emet ak eng' ngeguusyegap nyanjet. 
2  [
2  ] Ak poisyonik tugul che po kimnateennyi ak kamugennyi, ak ng'aleek tugul che po ooindap Mordekai ko uu ye ki ieet laitoryat ineendet ko ki kisirchi bukuitap ateptap peetuusyek ne po laitorinigap Media ak Persia. 
3  [
3  ] Amu ki ek Mordekai Yahudyot pounindet ne rubei Laitoryat Ahaseurus, ak ki oo ineendet eng' Yahudik. Ki chamak eng' tupchosyekyik che chaang' amu ki cheeng' ak koboisyechi piikyik eng' ooreet ne myee, ak kong'alaaljin iyotennyi tugul agobo kaalyeet. 
4  [
3  a] Ki le Mordekai, Yaei chu tugul Kamuktaindet. 
5  [
3  b] Abwaati karwotitoet ne ki anyooru agobo tukyu ne ma mi kiy ne tomo kosulda: 
6  [
3  c] Segeneniat ne ki ek aineet, lapkeiyet ne ki iluu, asiista, mogoochek. Esta ko aineet - inee ne ki itun laitoryat ak koyai koek osotyotap laitoryat. 
7  [
3  d] Tyong'ik che eech aeng' ko Haman ak anee. 
8  [
3  e] Pororyosyek ko icheek che ki ituiyogei kobuuch kainetap Yahudyot. 
9  [
3  f] Pororyet agenge, nenyu, ko Israel, icheek che ki riirchi Kamuktaindet ak ki kisar. Wei, ki kosor piikyik Kamuktaindet ak koistoe yaitwogichu tugul, ki koyai kwang'ut ak kaboorunoik Kamuktaindet che tomo kogeerei poror age tugul. 
10  [
3  g] “Ki kochop kayomisutik aeng', agenge ne po piikyik ak age ne po pororyosyek tugul. 
11  [
3  h] Ki kechop kayomisutichu si kotwoiso eng' sait, eng' kasarta ak eng' peetuut ne ki kochop Kamuktaindet agobo pororyosyek. 
12  [
3  i] Ki kobwaat Kamuktaindet eng' niito piikyik ak kotoroor icheek; 
13  [
3  k] ak eng' peetuusyechuuto, peetuutap taman ak ang'wan ak taman ak muut ne po arawetap Adar, koek peetuusyegap tuiyet, poiboiyet, ak kagasetapkei eng' taitap Kamuktaindet, eng' ibinwek tugul ak eng' piikyik Israel koigeny.” 
14  [
3  l] Ki kiip parwaani po Purim eng' kenyiitap ang'wan ne po pounatetap Ptolemy ak Kleopatra, Dositheus, inee ne ki igimit kole tisiin ak ko po kootap Lawi, ak Ptolemy weeriinnyi. Ki cheeng' imandanyi, kowelel Lysimakus weeriitap Ptolemy, agenge eng' meng'iigap Jerusalem.

